    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3083740/extras/5b644a8fa0de4b81ba639dbd8011bc9e.avif?t=1764252066\" width=437 height=162 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Smash your way to victory in this hilariously addictive, feature packed, multiplayer party game. With game modes such as &quot;Hide &amp; Seek&quot;, &quot;Rock Racing&quot;, &quot;Tag&quot;, &quot;Battle Royale&quot; and more, Rocks will have you screaming at your friends, crying with laughter and hanging on to the edge of your seat!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >All your friends are busy? Why not race around the Rock Karts track to beat your best lap time or battle your way through waves of AI Rock champions in our Single Player Modes. Use skilfully crafted weapons and armour to smash through your enemies and earn your fortune in pebbles to carve your name in Rocks history! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3083740/extras/339fcbb22c67b5f467b4ee29825661cb.avif?t=1764252066\" width=646 height=147 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Host your own lobby of up to 6 players</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Complete achievements to unlock special items</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Customise your Golem with items you've unlocked to bring out your inner ROCK!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Battle waves of AI Rock champions in the battle arena (Single Player Mode) and earn pebbles to spend in the item shop</p></li></ul>",
